, designated by 
<bibRefCitation id="BFDC05B6D6EEA0D3AC7C4AC5EA546B28" DOI="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1095-8339.1990.tb02227.x" author="Knapp, S" journalOrPublisher="Botanical Journal of the Linnean Society" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="113 - 139" refId="B127" refString="Knapp, S, Jarvis, CE, 1990. The typification of the names of New World Solanum species described by Linnaeus. Botanical Journal of the Linnean Society 104 (4): 113 - 139, DOI: https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1095-8339.1990.tb02227.x" title="The typification of the names of New World Solanum species described by Linnaeus." url="https://doi.org/10.1111/j.1095-8339.1990.tb02227.x" volume="104" year="1990">Knapp and Jarvis 1990</bibRefCitation>
